Odaily Planet Daily News Messari released Solana's 2024 Q4 report, which disclosed: 
Solana ecosystem DeFi TVL reached 8.6 billion US dollars (+64%), surpassing Tron to become the second largest public chain, with on-chain application revenue of 840 million US dollars (+213%); 
Solana ecosystem's average daily DEX trading volume is 3.3 billion US dollars (+150%), and Jupiter accounts for 38% of the market share, mainly due to Memecoin and AI token transactions; 
Solana ecosystem stablecoin market value is 5.1 billion US dollars (+36%), USDC accounts for 75%, and USDT increases to 912 million US dollars. 
In addition, Visa expands SolanaUSDC settlement, and Grayscale submits SolanaETF application. Overall, Solana ecosystem growth is strong and institutional adoption is accelerating.
